Humans are an ecosystem, not an organism. Made up of trillions of organisms living on and inside our bodies. Affecting and interacting in more ways than we can imagine.
At Rejuvome, we strongly believe in this philosophy, and hence are studying the microbial ecosystem within the human body; finding novel ways through which we can harness it for Rejuvenation and Longevity.  

We aim to lead the innovation in the field of microbiome therapeutics and find novel ways to harness it for Rejuvenation and Longevity.  
Our Mission
Transform the way we age by harnessing microbiome research to deliver personalized, life-enhancing solutions.
Our Vision
Lead the age of microbiome-driven rejuvenation, where gut health rewrites the rules of ageing.
